- Root routes: `app.routes.ts` — `AppShellComponent` wraps guest routes + lazy portal trees with `portalMatchGuard`
- Guest routes: `guest/guest.routes.ts` — flat pages: `/` portal picker, `/login`, `/register`, `/admin/login`
- Portal routes: `portal/user/user.routes.ts`, `portal/admin/admin.routes.ts`
- App URLs + portal kind: `shared/constants/app-urls.ts` (barrel), `guest-urls.ts`, `user-urls.ts`, `admin-urls.ts`, `portal-kind.type.ts` — **never hardcode route paths**; see `.cursor/rules/app-urls.mdc`
- Shared data: `shared/constants/bih-cities.ts` (`BIH_CITY_OPTIONS`); `shared/constants/boolean-filter-options.ts` (`BOOLEAN_FILTER_OPTIONS` — yes/no option tiles); `shared/constants/user-entity-status.ts` (`UserEntityStatus` — interim); `shared/constants/entity-context-class.ts` (`entityContextClass()`); portal icons: `portal/admin/admin-page-icons.ts`, `portal/user/user-page-icons.ts` — see `shared-constants.mdc`, `entity-status.mdc`, `entity-service-colors.mdc`
- Shared utils: `shared/utils/date-input.ts`, `shared/utils/format-display-date.ts`, `shared/utils/normalize-for-search.ts`, `shared/utils/hub-tab-sync.ts` — see `shared-utils.mdc`
- Auth: `shared/core/auth/` — session types (`AuthUser`, `Session` in `auth.model.ts`); stub login until API; company registration stub in `guest/pages/register/register-company.service.ts`
- Guards: `guest/guards/guest.guard.ts` (`guestGuard`); `portal/guards/portal-match.guard.ts`
- Portal config: `portal/common/models/portal-config.model.ts`, `portal/user/user-portal.config.ts`, `portal/admin/admin-portal.config.ts`; topbar nav: `portal/user/user-topbar-nav.config.ts`
- App shell: `shared/shell/` — `AppShellComponent`, `AppTopbarComponent`; topbar: theme → language → (notifications + account when authenticated)
