- Forms: `shared/form/` (barrel `index.ts`); Tables: `shared/table/` (barrel `index.ts`); Confirm: `shared/confirm/` (`ConfirmService`, global `ConfirmDialogComponent` in `app.html`)
- Features: `portal/user/features/` (home marketplace hub, our-listings, transport, freight, warehouse); `portal/admin/features/` (home hub, settings, users, vehicles, warehouses)
