- Theme/breakpoints: `src/styles.scss`, `src/styles/_portal-accent.scss` (guest picker/login/register only), `src/styles/_entity-service-accent.scss`, `src/styles/_table-chrome-split-card.scss`, `src/styles/_interaction.scss`, `src/styles/_breakpoints.scss`, `shared/constants/viewport.ts` (`MOBILE_MEDIA_QUERY`)
- Shared UI widgets: `shared/ui/` — brand-mark, **theme-picker** / **language-picker** (single-click toggles; language shows EN/BS), entity-tabs, page-title, page-back-link, page-header, primary-action-link, **detail-page-layout**, **entity-detail-summary**, **detail-action-bar**, route-display, date-range-display, **date-period-picker**, vehicle-display, warehouse-display, status-badge
- Topbar create menu: `shared/shell/app-topbar/entity-create-menu/` — `EntityCreateMenuComponent` (`+` beside brand; user + admin)

## Auth routing (guards)

| Guard | Where | Behavior |
|-------|-------|----------|
| `guestGuard` | `/`, `/login`, `/register`, `/admin/login` | Unauthenticated → allow; authenticated → session portal home |
| `portalMatchGuard` | `''` and `admin` lazy trees | Unauthenticated → `/`; wrong portal → correct portal home |

## Layout behavior (do not reimplement ad hoc)

- **Single shell:** `AppShellComponent` — topbar + scrollable `.app-shell__content` for all routes (no portal accent host class)
- **User topbar:** plain **BHCOM** brand → marketplace home (`USER_HOME_URL`); **`EntityCreateMenuComponent`** (`+` beside brand) → create URLs (`shared.topbar.offer.openMenu`); account **Moje objave** / **My listings** (`LucideListChecks`) → `userOurListingsUrl()`
- **Admin topbar:** **BHCOM** + neutral **ADMIN** suffix (`portal.shell.admin.badge`, `--text-muted`)
- **Main scroll:** `.app-shell__content`

